Drop sRGB_IEC61966-2-1_black_scaled.icc in this directory.

Source: https://www.color.org/srgbprofiles.xalter

The ColorProfile manipulator (src/Glide/ColorProfile.php) reads the file at
resources/icc/sRGB_IEC61966-2-1_black_scaled.icc and applies it to every
transformed image on the Imagick driver, converting the image's source
colorspace (Adobe RGB, Display P3, CMYK, etc.) to sRGB via lcms.

If the file is absent, the manipulator silently no-ops and delivery continues
unchanged — the addon does not break.
